// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/MXlfRB sphere intersection construction, 2024 by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/M3lBRS sphere sphere intersection
// using https://www.shadertoy.com/view/MffcWr oriented ring

// Construction of exact euclidean SDF of the intersection of two spheres.
// The intersection of two spheres (green and blue) forms a lens-shaped object (yellow).
// The max-operator is used when inside either cone (grey).
// Outside both cones SDF is a circle (red).

// Different SDFs must be joined where perpendicular to surface!

// Additional thickness added for visualization.

// Verified exactness in SDF debugger:
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/43fBz2 sphere intersection verification

// tags: ray, sphere, intersection, marching, geometry, construction

